240
00:20:06,223 --> 00:20:10,433
You're very lucky to have so rich
and hospitable an ex-pupil.

241
00:20:10,594 --> 00:20:13,302
Oh, I don't know, Max.
Charlie was a very nice boy.

242
00:20:13,463 --> 00:20:15,841
