355
00:26:56,666 --> 00:26:59,112
Oh, but you came
to see the show especially tonight.

356
00:26:59,269 --> 00:27:00,373
My fifth time.

357
00:27:00,537 --> 00:27:02,744
This is Chips.
I told you about him, remember?

358
00:27:02,906 --> 00:27:03,976
Of course.

359
00:27:04,140 --> 00:27:05,983
